{
  "id": "adv_main_01_01_05",
  "title": "星見編1章6話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "この子と組むのは嫌です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just don’t put me in the same group with her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7340362548828123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "なんとなく前を通ったから\nこの事務所に入ったって聞きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you just happened to walk by Hoshimi Productions\nand that’s why you joined.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.767369588216146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そんないい加減な気持ちの人と\n一緒にやりたくはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no intention of being in a group\nwith someone who has such a careless attitude.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.60070292154948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "いい加減って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "careless attitude.?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.70070292154948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いい加減でしょ？　どれだけの子が\nアイドルに憧れて、努力してると思ってるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ careless attitude‚ aren't you? Do you have any idea\nhow many girls fight tooth and nail to become an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.86736958821615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あなたみたいな\n思いつきで入ってきていい世界じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn’t a world\nwhere you can just randomly decide to join.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.400702921549478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "……思いつきじゃないよ、私、本気\n本気でアイドルになろうと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I didn’t randomly decide. I’m serious.\nI really do want to become an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.00070292154948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.56736958821615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "私もずっと探してたの……ここを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been searching for this place for a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "？\n……どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\n…What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tears-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 46
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、心臓病でね\n三年前、心臓移植してるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ I’ve got a heart condition.\nSo I had a heart transplant three years ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それで……ライブバトルなんて、大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait a minute… You sure you can handle live battles?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "うん、体の方はもう全然大丈夫\n走っても、夜更かししても、遠くに出かけても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. I’m all healthy now.\nI can run all day‚ stay up all night‚ travel far away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "前みたいに疲れて倒れたりすることはなくなって\n凄く幸せだったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t get exhausted and collapse like I used to.\nI was so happy to get a new heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "でも……この心臓が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… this new heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "何かしたがっているの、やり残したことがあるって……\nそう言ってる気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s got dreams of its own—unfinished business.\nThat’s what it seems to be telling me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "だから、それを見つけてあげたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to help it find what it’s looking for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "ドキンって胸が鳴る方に向かっていったり\n胸がわくわくするようなことをやってみたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I go where it tells me to go‚\nwhatever makes it skip a beat or flutter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それで……星見プロダクションに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… that’s what brought you to Hoshimi Productions?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "入った瞬間に分かったの\nああ、ここだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The moment I set foot here‚ I knew.\nI knew that this was the place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "この胸が、来たかったのは\nやりたいことがあるのはここだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is where my heart longed to be.\nWhere it had unfinished business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（恐らく、本気でずっと探していたんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She must’ve been searching all this time.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（自分を助けてくれた心臓の願いが分からず）\n（罪悪感を覚えていたのかもしれない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Perhaps it was survivor’s guilt）\n（at not knowing her donor’s dying wish.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（答えてくれない自分の胸に、常人では）\n（想像出来ないような不安を抱いてもいただろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The silence of her own heart）\n（must’ve consumed her with unimaginable anxiety.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、まだ本当にそうなのか分からない……\nもしかしたら違うかもしれない、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I know I could be wrong about this.\nThis whole thing might not be true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんを見て思った\nやってみようって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I saw you‚ Kotono-chan‚\nit made me want to give it a shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "私と同じように\n出来るか分からないけど頑張ってる人がいるなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I knew that if there were someone\nwho's doing the best‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "一緒に頑張ってみようって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to give it a try together and work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "………………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "――言葉はいらなかった\n琴乃に向けて。未来に向けて二人の手が結ばれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――No words are needed.\nToward Kotono. Toward the future. Their hands held.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
